	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>City of Lafayette adjoining New Orleans La.</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>November 9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1849</date> corresponding with the <date>23<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> day of<lb/>Heshvan 5610</date>.</p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><addressee>Isaac Leeser Esqre.</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Editor of the Occident.&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir.</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">The Israelites of this place have added one<lb/> more place of worship dedicated to the Supreme Ruler of the Universe&#59; &#8212;&#8220;The<lb/> Great and holy One of <persName>Jacob</persName>.&#8221;&#8212;Under the name and style of <hi rend="underline">Dover tof</hi>.<lb/>  It is to be hoped that our march is onward&#59; &#8212;Although our number here is<lb/> at present but small we have a <sic>fare</sic> prospect of increase.  We have <sic>temporar&#8222;<lb/>&#8222; ry</sic> only rented a house for a place of worship&#44; and number about forty families<lb/> who were previous compelled to attend the Synagogue in <placeName>New Orleans</placeName> a<lb/> distance of about two miles from the Centre of <placeName>Lafayette</placeName>.&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I hope soon to be able to give a better account of ourselves&#44; as<lb/> we are about to make a move among our brethren Israelites&#44; to collect<lb/> sufficient funds to purchase a lot of Ground and build a Synagogue.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">At a meeting held last <date>Sunday November 4th 1849</date>.  The following<lb/> officers were duly elected to serve for the balance of the year <date>5610</date>.  viz<lb/> <persName role="author">Abraham de Young</persName> President  <persName>Jacob Meyer</persName> Vice President <persName>H. Asher</persName>&#44;<lb/> <persName>Benjm. Goldenberg</persName> and <persName>B. Frank</persName>&#44; Trustees&#44; <persName>N. Grunsburger</persName> Treasurer&#44; and <persName>Julius Layn</persName> Secretary&#8212;we have adopted German <hi rend="underline">minnic</hi>.&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The above information is respectfully submitted for the use of your<lb/> valuable monthly periodical by</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)">Your obt. &#38; Humble Servant.</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><persName role="author">Abraham de Young</persName></p>
